[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "できたっ！\n『避雷のペンダント』！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01570",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そのペンダントをつけていると\n雷を受け流せるのね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01571",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、これがあれば雷鳴の島で\n雷が落ちても大丈夫だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01572",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ただ、どれくらい数を用意できるか……\n全員分用意するのは難しいかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01573",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんまり待たせるとヘルトの場合\n飽きて悪事をしでかしそうだし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01574",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、乗り込む準備もできてきたし、\nそろそろ誰が行くかを決めなくちゃね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01575",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私やレスナは当然行くとして……\nヤドヴィガとキューンはちょっと無理ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01576",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ごめん……あの二人と戦うのは、やっぱり……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01577",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いいのよ。私が強引に攫ってるんだから、\nお姉ちゃんに任せておきなさい！　あとは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01578",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "アルビーナのこと、だよね？\n分かってる。私に少し考えがあるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01579",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ねえ……ヤド姉。私たち、このままでいいのかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01580",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "九偉人同士の戦いは本来、\n我が主の望むところではない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01581",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "え？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01582",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "それを止めることは、我が主の意思には反しない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01583",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……うん。そうだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01584",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……というわけで、雷鳴の島に乗り込むのは私と\nヴァレリア、イザナちゃん、ハイディさん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01585",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それに九偉人組からはイェルカとシトリン。\nブラオールからはタイニーとエルス、ジョゼの三人",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01586",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "元錬金党からはジェロンとララ、\nそして、ティム君も参加するって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01587",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "それと、王国の威信に懸けてクリセルダたちに\n手出しさせないってユナさんが言ってたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01588",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヘルトさんたちが襲いに行くかもとは思ったけど、\nそれなら安心だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01589",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それじゃあ、人員の割り振りはこれで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01590",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "アルビーナ、本当にこれでいいの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01591",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はい。正直今のアタシは決戦に行っても\n足手まといっす。戦力分析はできているつもりです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01592",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そう……無理強いはできないしね。\nアルビーナの力を借りられないのは痛いんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01593",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "この上、足だけは引っ張りたくないんですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01594",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……そう、なら待ってて。\n圧勝して帰ってくるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01595",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、ベップさん。ちょっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01596",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01597",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "うん、分かった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01598",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "アルビーナが、過酷な環境や強大な敵のせいで\n心に傷を負っていたとはな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01599",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いやあほんと申し訳ないっす！\nみんなが鍛えてくれたし、場数も経験も積んだのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01600",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "暗黒の氷海の頃から成長したって自覚もあるのに……\n足が……すくんで動かないんすよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01601",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "自分なりに、より前に進めるよう、\n自信をつけられるよう、模索はしていたのですが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01602",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "今回には間に合わなかったです……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01603",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ほんと、こんなザマで英雄になりたいだなんて\n情けないったらありゃしない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01604",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様、今回の決戦は後方支援に徹しよう？\n私も、そばにいるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01605",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "前で戦うのだけが大事なんじゃない、\n補給や支援も大事だって騎士の教えにもあるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01606",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ん、理屈では分かってる、つもり。でも、\n後方支援とか中途半端に戦ってるからダメなのかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01607",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いっそまるっきり離れて、錬金術のこと\n考えるのやめようかな、なんて。あはは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01608",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "アタシの他にも、錬金術士はいることだしね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01609",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "なるほど、重症だな、これは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01610",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]